name: The HEN does not fly.
description:
In a troubled environment and an uncertain future ahead, we know we have to keep going. 

That's what we always do, we resist, we overcome, and we carry on... the important thing is to move forward. 

One day the hen made us believe that we could fly, but in a sad way we will remember that hen doesn't fly.
